thread.title: Protesters target Starbucks in Philadelphia over arrests of black men

title: Protesters target Starbucks in Philadelphia over arrests of black men
text:
Protesters target Starbucks in Philadelphia over arrests of black men 12:35pm IST - 01:11 
Racial tensions are running high in Philadelphia, where protesters on Sunday swarmed a Starbucks, where two black men were arrested last week. Nathan Frandino reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
